{
  "texts": [
    "For example, scholars usually explore debiasing techniques for removing inherent data bias and generate counterfactual examples to explain model prediction.To solve these issues, we offer a comprehensive mapping analysis of some recent fairness concerns and academics' proposed strategies.",
    "A comprehensive mapping study can present a clear idea of how to explore this field of research, which is especially helpful for aspiring scholars.",
    "Besides, a mapping study is a valuable tool for identifying and retrieving recent articles, facilitating the collection of related studies in subsequent years, even if the discussed articles become outdated.",
    "In this regard, the impact of a mapping study can endure longer than that of conventional review articles.",
    "Figure 1 graphically represents our motivation to follow a systematic mapping study."
  ]
}